The paper discusses the application of permissioned blockchain in the field of horizontal strategic alliances, which involves security and distributed systems (cs.CR). The proposed model includes a hierarchical structure and reputation mechanism, which are related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of reputation as a measure of reliability also involves machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the practical application of the proposed model, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE).
